data.description: Beautiful 4 bedroom, 3 bath, 3 car garage screened in 12'5x15' porch built in 2022 in Water Leaf.  This home is the popular Destin Floorplan offers spacious open concept living great for entertaining.  Kitchen has center island with granite counter tops, breakfast nook, separate dining, stainless steel appliance's, and large pantry. Large primary bedroom & bathroom with a 5' x 12' 4" walk in closet, double vanity, garden tub & large separate shower. Home has granite throughout. Beautiful wood look engineered vinyl plank flooring throughout main areas and Frieze carpet in the bedrooms. Fabric hurricane window & door protection included.  You will love the screened in porch with fenced in back yard for outdoor entertaining. Home is located on a cul-de-sac. Convenient E. Gulf Breeze (Midway) location easy drive to beaches, Pensacola, Navarre, NAS and more.
